metadata.name: Forest Android
metadata.description:
- Year : 2550.
- Description : civilization has evolved and distanced itself from nature in such a way that it is impossible for human beings to leave the big cities. Viruses and diseases that spread in forests that were natural hundreds of years ago, are now deadly for the human race.
Robots have been created to investigate the evolution of these forests and jungles, since the evolution that has occurred within them is totally unknown.
- Location : Enchanted Forest, Canada.

Android created with artificial intelligence.

2454 x 2381
